{"tid":2420093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"王婆婆昨晩被捕後今晩踢保 警方保留檢控權利 交由重案組跟進","createTime":"2021-02-23T16:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T11:27:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd233bb16850f877746691bc94249c88faa41d5","tid":2420093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"【周二（23日） - 22:50】王婆婆被扣留一日後，至周二晚上10時警方表示王婆婆拒絕保釋，獲暫時釋放，警方保留檢控權利。案件交由將軍澳警區重案組第二隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n周一（22日）是陳彥霖逝世第17個月，警方在尚德邨停車場對出十字路口嚴陣以待。晚上7時許，示威常客64歲王婆婆王鳳瑤，帶同黃色小雨傘、一束白花以及寫有「真相：節錄&ne;全部」的標語，自行來到尚十叫喊口號，其後被警員截查。其後，警方指王婆婆行為引致群眾鼓噪，將她以涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢拘捕，帶至將軍澳警署扣留調查，案件正由將軍澳警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210222/WVLMXZ7JZZHE7HZ3JACTHC2YUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210222%2FWVLMXZ7JZZHE7HZ3JACTHC2YUM%2F&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpm5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=cdc275e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210222%2FWVLMXZ7JZZHE7HZ3JACTHC2YUM%2F&h=f5dc42fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210222/WVLMXZ7JZZHE7HZ3JACTHC2YUM/</a>"},{"pid":"d4ab83c9fb604b734930e9708ebba1e2d4fcebc2","tid":2420093,"uid":134683,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"婆婆好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0799e85960f589bb1f8044d8b11e91eaff5151fc","tid":2420093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac